Skogen Cosmetics is a Swedish brand that designs & manufactures its own cosmetic products. The Skogen team has over 15 years of experience in the cosmetic industry and the owner itself has a PhD in chemistry.
The company strongly focuses on quality and produces high end luxury products that at the same time are environmentally friendly and healthy. The Skogen motto is "Beauty by Nature".
If you are interested in more information don't hesistate to contact us or visit our website 
